  "description" : "Seiran Island, the tropical remote island, is home to http://anidb.net/ch145452 [Tachibana Junnosuke] and his young sister, http://anidb.net/ch145456 [Asane], who return here from the mainland as a result of their parents` death. However, Seiran Island has become a dystopia where, to stop the decline of population, authorities have enforced the \"Pervert Law.\" Sex is permitted and encouraged anywhere on the island, and those who refuse any sexual acts will be punished as a criminal offense. Being a cherry-picker who takes pride in his virginity, Junnosuke is skeptical about the law, thus, he sets up an anti-mating force, NLNS (No Love No Sex) to protect himself and his innocent sister, making headway to destroy the perverted law!\nSource: OceanVeil\nNote: The first three episodes received an early screening at a special event on 22 June 2025 at Cinem@rt Shinjuku in Tokyo. The regular TV broadcast started on 19 July 2025.\nNote: The anime has 3 versions - fully regulated version for regular TV audiences, less censored streaming-only version, and the least regulated \"Seiran Island\" version distributed on AT-X and Blu-ray.",
